profile: Smart film, also called Switchable film, is a product that is capable of adjusting light transmission between transparent and opaque using AC power. Our UL Recognized Smart Film converts your windows, doors, divider walls, skylights and partitions to provide an incredible combination of natural light, comfort, security & energy efficiency.
